<!here|@here>  with the Latest commit 488d266  issue #1131 — moving main.go to fabric/peer.  You may encounter the problem in vagrant:
```vagrant@hyperledger-devenv:v0.0.9-2457c97:/opt/gopath/src/github.com/hyperledger/fabric$ cd peer/
-bash: cd: peer/: Not a directory```
It seems vagrant caches the `peer` exe file. The solution is to run:
```vagrant halt
vagrant up
```
